125
0:09:36.731,000 --> 0:09:4,000
My exact job title is "ink formulation scientist."

126
0:09:41.633,000 --> 0:09:45,000
But I don't work on the ink that you use for your writing pens.

127
0:09:46.366,000 --> 0:09:48,000
