140
0:10:35.686,000 --> 0:10:38,000
Here, we are talking about a different space

141
0:10:38.972,000 --> 0:10:4,000
from the bubbles I'd seen in Paris.

142
0:10:42.96,000 --> 0:10:44,000
The bubbles that are trapped inside those inks

143
0:10:45.186,000 --> 0:10:47,000
vary between a few millimeters,

144
0:10:48.141,000 --> 0:10:49,000
a few microns

145
0:10:49.408,000 --> 0:10:51,000
